.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-TOTAL-CAPACITY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-total-capacity \- show total capacity across active channels
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-total-capacity
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the sum of all active channel capacities.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"total_capacity_msat":N, "total_capacity_sat":N, "active_channels":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-local-balance (1),
.BR lightning-node-channel-count (1)
